# Logs Directory
# This directory stores all execution logs from the toolkit
#
# Log file: eht.log
# Contains all console output with timestamps and log levels
#
# Log levels:
#   INFO     - General information
#   SUCCESS  - Successful operations
#   WARNING  - Non-critical issues
#   ERROR    - Operation failures
#   DEBUG    - Detailed debugging info (when enabled)
#
# Log rotation: Log file appends indefinitely
# Consider logrotate or manual cleanup for long-term use
